challenging and it's not an isolated case, like that happens a lot,

00:29:11.199 --> 00:29:19.199
but at the end of the day, there is a solution for that, we can just work around that.

00:29:19.760 --> 00:29:26.800
I don't know about a challenging problem that we probably find out a solution,

00:29:27.760 --> 00:29:35.359
I mean as an IT as a whole, I don't know, I will think about that and if I think I'm

